As a restaurant owner, what are some seating arrangements that I can implement to maximize occupancy while ensuring that each table has at least 2 and at most 6 seats? Please provide 3 options in the following JSON format:
{
  "arrangement1": {
    "table1": 2,
    "table2": 4,
    "table3": 6,
    ...
  },
  "arrangement2": {
    "table1": 4,
    "table2": 4,
    "table3": 4,
    ...
  },
  "arrangement3": {
    "table1": 2,
    "table2": 2,
    "table3": 6,
    ...
  }
}
Please ensure that each arrangement option satisfies the minimum and maximum seating requirements for each table.
